{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3120ada3d","title":"毛泽东对中央农村工作部关于第二次全国农村工作会议报告的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4081206678","index":0,"year":1954,"month":6,"day":7,"articleId":"a3120ada3d"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1909181fe9","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对中央农村工作部关于第二次全国农村工作会议报告的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"77c74a1704","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"e58db86bd0","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"e9bdcec49a","type":"appellation","text":"刘少奇、邓子恢同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"d99731631d","type":"paragraph","text":"在第三页上作了一点修改，请酌定。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"d77fce08e9","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东六月七日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"a69b5cf5c6","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"1d1568a14d","type":"paragraph","text":"[这种有计划地大量增产的要求和小农经济分散私有的性质]以及农业技术的落后性质[之间的矛盾是越来越明显了，困难越来越多了。这是]两个[带根本性的矛盾。解决]这些[矛盾的]第一个方针，[就是实行]社会革命，[即农业合作化，就]必须把劳动农民[个人所有制逐步过渡到集体所有制，逐步过渡到社会主义。]第二个方针，就是实行技术革命，即在农业中逐步使用机器和实行其他技术改革。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"5feb7d8d5f","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"5c2bada00a","type":"paragraph","text":"[提高单位面积产量，是目前农业增产的主要出路。但要发挥这种增产潜在力，靠小农经济是有限的，靠]在农业中实行大规模的[机械化是工业发展以后的远景，在最近几年之内必须依靠大力发展农业合作化]，在合作化的基础上适当地进行各种可能的技术改革。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"},{"id":"c2a5bc68e2","type":"paragraph","text":"注：[  ]外为毛泽东加写或改写的文字。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d"}],"page":{"id":"a932927202","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a3120ada3d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}